  <h2>Development setup</h2>
  <p>If you want to build from source or contribute to PicFast:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Go 1.26+, Node 20+, pnpm, PostgreSQL 16, Git</li>
    <li><strong>Start services:</strong> <code>make docker-up</code> (launches PostgreSQL + Mailpit)</li>
    <li><strong>Run backend:</strong> <code>go run ./cmd/picfast</code></li>
    <li><strong>Run frontend:</strong> <code>cd web && pnpm install && pnpm dev</code></li>
  </ul>
  <p>Database migrations run automatically on startup. For bundled serving: <code>cd web && pnpm build && go run ./cmd/picfast</code>.</p>
  <p>See the <a href="https://github.com/atbeta/picfast/blob/main/README.en.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub README</a> for full development instructions.</p>
</DocsLayout>
